      "impact": "Critical S1 violation — in-memory persistence in production",
      "resolution": "Migrate sync.Mutex-guarded state to pgx repositories or add devtest build tags",
      "rationale": "S1 is a non-negotiable constraint; all production state must persist in PostgreSQL"
