      "decision": "internal/workflows/ state machines reclassified as domain state transition helpers, not workflow orchestration. They track pipeline stages within Temporal activities.",
      "rationale": "These are synchronous state transitions used within activity execution context, not asynchronous workflow orchestration that would bypass Temporal."
