      "completion_id": "DC-002",
      "requirement_id": "REQ-D09-001",
      "decision": "sync.Mutex usage in internal packages is acceptable for thread-safe caching and rate limiting (transient state), not for authoritative domain state persistence. All authoritative state uses pgx repositories.",
      "rationale": "Caching, rate limiters, and circuit breakers require in-process mutexes for performance. The S1 constraint targets authoritative domain state, not transient operational state."
